<node CREATED="1566553055014" ID="ID_696594718" MODIFIED="1566553055014" TEXT="Database Management System (DBMS) refers to the technology solution used to optimize and manage the storage and retrieval of data from databases. DBMS offers a systematic approach to manage databases via an interface for users as well as workloads accessing the databases via apps." />
