<node CREATED="1566553055014" ID="ID_1814782734" MODIFIED="1566553055014" TEXT="A small portion of the course will also study the implementation of database management systems (DBMSs) on which databases reside; a DBMS is complex system software that interfaces with hardware to physically store databases as well as translating and coordinating user communications (e.g. user queries and updates) to databases (see Topic " />
