<node CREATED="1566553055014" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1043584801" LINK="https://beginnersbook.com/2015/04/dbms-introduction/" MODIFIED="1566553055014" TEXT="Introduction to DBMS - BeginnersBook.com">
<node CREATED="1566553055014" ID="ID_923325991" MODIFIED="1566553055014" TEXT="We can break it like this DBMS = Database + Management System. Database is a collection of data and Management System is a set of programs to store and retrieve those data. Based on this we can define DBMS like this: DBMS is a collection of inter-related data and set of programs to store  access those data in an easy and effective manner." />
</node>
