<node CREATED="1566553055015" ID="ID_269778822" MODIFIED="1566553055015" TEXT="DBMS Introduction - A database management system (DBMS) refers to the technology for creating and managing databases. basically DBMS is a software tool to organize (create retrieve update and manage) data in a database. Web Design. HTML Tutorials Online HTML CSS and JS Editor Bootstrap 4 Tutorials." />
