<node CREATED="1566553055103" ID="ID_307552912" MODIFIED="1566553055103" TEXT="Introduction. Big data is a blanket term for the non-traditional strategies and technologies needed to gather organize process and gather insights from large datasets. While the problem of working with data that exceeds the computing power or storage of a single computer is not new the pervasiveness scale and value of this type of computing has greatly expanded in recent years." />
