<node CREATED="1566553055015" ID="ID_1276551087" MODIFIED="1566553055015" TEXT="The purpose of a database is to store and retrieve information in a way that is accurate and effective. The purpose for a database management system is to provide a system to manage the different databases it contains (performance security avai" />
