<node CREATED="1566553055016" ID="ID_1670529663" MODIFIED="1566553055016" TEXT="Database Management System &#226;&#8364;&#8220; The world of data is constantly changing and evolving every second. This in turn has created a completely new dimension of growth and challenges for companies around the globe. By accurately recording data updating and tracking them on an efficient and regular basis " />
