<node CREATED="1566553055016" ID="ID_351458793" MODIFIED="1566553055016" TEXT="2 Database System Concepts 1.3 &#194;&#169;Silberschatz Korth and Sudarshan Purpose of Database System In the early days database applications were built on top of file systems Drawbacks of using file systems to store data: &#226;&#732;&#8230; Data redundancy and inconsistency Multiple file formats duplication of information in different files &#226;&#732;&#8230; Difficulty in accessing data" />
