<node CREATED="1566553055020" ID="ID_1686256406" MODIFIED="1566553055020" TEXT="SQL Developer Data Modeler is a free graphical tool that allows you to create browse and edit logical relational physical multi-dimensional and data type models enhancing productivity and simplifying data modeling tasks." />
