<node CREATED="1566553055028" ID="ID_343578454" MODIFIED="1566553055028" TEXT="A data definition or data description language (DDL) is a syntax similar to a computer programming language for defining data structures especially database schemas.DDL statements create modify and remove database objects such as tables indexes and users. Common DDL statements are CREATE ALTER and DROP" />
