<node CREATED="1566553055029" ID="ID_59034593" MODIFIED="1566553055029" TEXT="A data manipulation language (DML) is a computer programming language used for adding (inserting) deleting and modifying (updating) data in a database. A DML is often a sublanguage of a broader database language such as SQL with the DML comprising some of the operators in the language." />
