<node CREATED="1566553055029" ID="ID_315672280" MODIFIED="1566553055029" TEXT="A data manipulation language (DML) is a family of computer languages including commands permitting users to manipulate data in a database. This manipulation involves inserting data into database tables retrieving existing data deleting data from existing tables and modifying existing data." />
