<node CREATED="1566553055029" ID="ID_1983223046" MODIFIED="1566553055029" TEXT="Using GRANT and REVOKE. Data Control Language(DCL) is used to control privileges in Database. To perform any operation in the database such as for creating tables sequences or views a user needs privileges. Privileges are of two types System: This includes permissions for creating session table etc and all types of other system privileges." />
