<node CREATED="1566553055017" ID="ID_439903776" MODIFIED="1566553055017" TEXT="Using a database management system (DBMS) calls/queries are made to retrieve the information. This part is called the back-end. To present the data in a consequential way to the user web developers create a web site and easy to use database applications. This part is called the front-end." />
