<node CREATED="1566553055022" ID="ID_276743416" MODIFIED="1566553055022" TEXT="The ER model defines the conceptual view of a database. It works around real-world entities and the associations among them. At view level the ER model is considered a good option for designing databases. An entity can be a real-world object either animate or inanimate that can be easily " />
