<node CREATED="1566553055027" ID="ID_1391359527" MODIFIED="1566553055027" TEXT="Before learning more in SQL you should know its advantages and disadvantages. So let&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s have a look at them - Advantages of SQL - * You don&#226;&#8364;&#8482;t need any coding in SQL. This means by using standard SQL you can easily manage database systems no need" />
