<node CREATED="1566553055027" ID="ID_81231196" MODIFIED="1566553055027" TEXT="Advantages of SQL. There are the following advantages of SQL: High speed. Using the SQL queries the user can quickly and efficiently retrieve a large amount of records from a database. No coding needed. In the standard SQL it is very easy to manage the database system. It doesnt require a substantial amount of code to manage the database system." />
