<node CREATED="1566553055033" ID="ID_841688891" MODIFIED="1566553055033" TEXT="SQL CREATE VIEW: A VIEW is a data object which contains no data. Its contents are the resultant of base table. The VIEW can be treated as a base table and it can be QUERIED UPDATED INSERTED INTO DELETED FROM and JOINED with other tables and views." />
