<node CREATED="1566553055033" ID="ID_982022008" MODIFIED="1566553055033" TEXT="SQL  Data Definition Language (DDL)  Create View Statement. Views can be considered as virtual tables. Generally speaking a table has a set of definition and it physically stores the data. A view also has a set of definitions which is build on top of table(s) or other view(s) and it does not physically store the data." />
