<node CREATED="1566553055048" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1542992951" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Relational_database" MODIFIED="1566553055048" TEXT="Relational database - Wikipedia">
<node CREATED="1566553055048" ID="ID_810329074" MODIFIED="1566553055048" TEXT="A relational database is a digital database based on the relational model of data as proposed by E. F. Codd in 1970. A software system used to maintain relational databases is a relational database management system (RDBMS). Virtually all relational database systems use SQL (Structured Query Language) for querying and maintaining the database." />
