<node CREATED="1566553055048" ID="ID_1938751212" MODIFIED="1566553055048" TEXT="A domain is a unique set of values permitted for an attribute in a table. For example a domain of month-of-year can accept January February&#226;&#8364;&#166;.December as possible values a domain of integers can accept whole numbers that are negative positive and zero. Definition: Domain constraints are user defined data type and we can define them like this:" />
