<node CREATED="1566553055018" ID="ID_1815954507" MODIFIED="1566553055018" TEXT="I think you want the simplest easiest-to-do solution for your project. You don&#226;&#8364;&#8482;t want to get bogged down with complicated programming. The simplest easiest (SQL) database is SQLite. It is more than sufficient for your needs. Databases like MySQL" />
