<node CREATED="1566553055018" ID="ID_1641217281" MODIFIED="1566553055018" TEXT="Data Definition Language. Data Definition Language (DDL) statements are used to classify the database structure or schema. It is a type of language that allows the DBA or user to depict and name those entities attributes and relationships that are required for the application along with any associated integrity and security constraints." />
</node>
