<node CREATED="1566553055054" ID="ID_1704590364" MODIFIED="1566553055054" TEXT="This is the fourth in a series of posts teaching normalization. The third post focused on the second normal form its definition and examples to hammer it home.. Once a table is in second normal form we are guaranteed that every column is dependent on the primary key or as I like to say the table serves a single purpose." />
