<node CREATED="1566553055056" ID="ID_292877035" MODIFIED="1566553055056" TEXT="A temporal entity is an entity that models the period of time when a row is valid with respect to system time (or transaction time when the transaction is recorded) business time (or valid time when the data is valid with respect to information about the real world) or both.. To be considered valid the fact that is being modeled is only true during a certain period of time." />
</node>
