<node CREATED="1566553055056" ID="ID_1837542860" MODIFIED="1566553055056" TEXT="Summary. Modelling Spatial and Spatial-Temporal Data: A Bayesian Approach is aimed at statisticians and quantitative social economic and public health students and researchers who work with small-area spatial and spatial-temporal data. It assumes a grounding in statistical theory up to the standard linear regression model." />
</node>
