<node CREATED="1566553055097" ID="ID_207116947" MODIFIED="1566553055097" TEXT="A failure mode is a cause of failure or one possible way a system can fail. When a system has many potential ways of failing it has multiple failure modes or competing risks. The more complex a system is the more failure modes there are." />
</node>
