<node CREATED="1566553055097" ID="ID_1732036299" MODIFIED="1566553055097" TEXT="&#226;&#8224;&#8217; FMEA (Failure Mode and Effects Analysis) is an Analytical Technique that combines the technology and Experience of People in identifying predictable failure modes of a Product or Process and planning for its elimination. FMEA can be explained as a group of activities intended to: Recognize and Evaluate the potential failure of a product or process and its effects." />
</node>
