<node CREATED="1566553055097" ID="ID_478616120" MODIFIED="1566553055097" TEXT="&#226;&#8364;&#339;Accept&#226;&#8364;&#65533; the failure mode cause. B. Describe an action for each failure mode cause that will eliminate or control it. C. Identify outcome measures that will be used to analyze and test the re-designed process." />
