<node CREATED="1566553055097" ID="ID_644784142" MODIFIED="1566553055097" TEXT="A non-blocking consensus protocol. The three-phase commit protocol is said to be non-blocking. The blocking nature of the two-phase commit protocol is alleviated by introducing one more phase [10].. 3PC splits the prepare state in two[2]." />
