<node CREATED="1566553055098" ID="ID_257826783" MODIFIED="1566553055098" TEXT="Distributed Concurrency Control There are different techniques used to manage the concurrency and hence the deadlock in the distributed Database systems. Primary Site Technique &#226;&#8364;&#8220; Here single database location is considered as primary site and is responsible for managing the transactions of the distributed database system." />
</node>
