<node CREATED="1566553055098" ID="ID_674147307" MODIFIED="1566553055098" TEXT="Most of the theory concerning concurrency control in databases is developed in terms of interleaved concurrency although it may be adapted to simultaneous concurrency. Genuine vs appearance of concurrency Concurrency is the ability of the database management system to process more than one transaction at a time." />
</node>
