<node CREATED="1566553055098" ID="ID_1456222965" MODIFIED="1566553055098" TEXT="NoSQL databases were created to overcome the limitations of relational databases. What is a NoSQL database? NoSQL databases are different than relational databases like MQSql. In relational database you need to create the table define schema set the data types of fields etc before you can actually insert the data. In NoSQL you don&#226;&#8364;&#8482;t have to " />
