<node CREATED="1566553055098" ID="ID_1158865874" MODIFIED="1566553055098" TEXT="Unraveling NoSQL and trying to explain what it is and whether youd be interested in it or not is difficult. This article aims to give a high level introduction to NoSQL and provides a comparison of the latest technologies in this space." />
