<node CREATED="1566553055098" ID="ID_87518495" MODIFIED="1566553055098" TEXT="Over the past few years large tech companies such as Netflix Hulu Uber and Facebook and have brought notoriety to NoSQL or non-relational databases. In this blog post I will give a brief&#226;&#8364;&#166;" />
