<node CREATED="1566553055101" ID="ID_134288323" MODIFIED="1566553055101" TEXT="The ACID properties and the CAP theorem are two important concepts in data management and distributed systems. It&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s unfortunate that in both acronyms the &#226;&#8364;&#339;C&#226;&#8364;&#65533; stands for &#226;&#8364;&#339;Consistency&#226;&#8364;&#65533; but actually means completely different things. What follows is a primer on the two concepts and an " />
