<node CREATED="1566553055101" ID="ID_1728978515" MODIFIED="1566553055101" TEXT="CAP theorem and databases: definitions of ACID Atomic  Distributed systems in theory and in practice. Thursday March 26 2015. The confusing CAP and ACID wording CAP and ACID share a common vocabulary: Atomic Consistent and so on.  That&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s not an objective for CAP. CAP is about the possible properties of multiple operations using the " />
</node>
