<node CREATED="1566553055102" ID="ID_1923896080" MODIFIED="1566553055102" TEXT="A NoSQL (originally referring to non SQL or non relational) database provides a mechanism for storage and retrieval of data that is modeled in means other than the tabular relations used in relational databases.Such databases have existed since the late 1960s but did not obtain the NoSQL moniker until a surge of popularity in the early 21st century triggered by the needs of Web 2.0 " />
