<node CREATED="1566553055102" ID="ID_944673838" MODIFIED="1566553055102" TEXT="NoSQL databases have introduced many innovations to address the limitations of traditional relational databases. Key among these innovations is a flexible data model able to support the large volume and variety of data being generated by modern applications." />
